nodes.title: Instructions:
widgets_values:
1. Mute InvertMask. -------------------->
2. Queue test frames (20-50).
3. Choose the correct masking colours for your subject. Use colour picker to check.
4. Un-mute InvertMask.
5. Enable/disable wanted outputs.
6. Set Project Name and output folder.
7. Queue.
